{{Hatnote|本文介绍的是电子学笑话，关于计算机工程中有实际意义的只写存储器，参见“{{link-en|只写存储器 (工程学)|Write-only memory (engineering)}}”。}}

'''只写存储器'''（{{lang-en|'''W'''rite-'''O'''nly '''M'''emory}}，缩写：'''WOM'''）是和[[只读存储器|只读存储器]]（ROM）相反的一种[[存储器|存储器]]。按照一些定义，只写存储器是一种只能被写入而永远不能读取的设备。因为一种只能写入还不能被读取的内存电路是没有任何实际用处的，因此这个概念经常被用作[[笑话|笑话]]或者对损坏的[[内存|内存]]设备的[[委婉|委婉]]修辞。这个术语的首次使用通常归因于1972年的[[西格尼蒂克|西格尼蒂克]]公司。因为内部的恶作剧，西格尼蒂克在那一年发表了一些关于只写内存的文章。后来，这个笑话在电子学界被经常提及<ref name="origin">{{cite web | url = http://portal.national.com/rap/Story/WOMorigin.html | title = The origin of the WOM – the "Write Only Memory" | first = Robert A | last = Pease | author-link = Bob Pease | publisher = National Semiconductor | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6AxYMnQNI?url=http://portal.national.com/rap/Story/WOMorigin.html | archivedate = 2012-09-26 | dead-url = yes }}.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/2011-04/02/content_12268630.htm | title = Are you fooled? | work = China Daily | date = 2011-04-02 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | archive-date = 2020-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200128020507/https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/2011-04/02/content_12268630.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并收录于软件工程学的词典中<ref name = Jargon>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930231240/http://catb.org/~esr/jargon/html/W/write-only-memory.html | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | archivedate = 2020-09-30 | url = http://www.catb.org/~esr/jargon/html/W/write-only-memory.html | title = write-only memory | work = The [[Jargon_File|Jargon File]] | publisher = CatB | editor-link = Eric S. Raymond | editor-last = Raymond | editor-first = Eric S | dead-url = no }}</ref>，列在最佳恶作剧集合单中。

== 西格尼蒂克公司 ==

只写存储器的数据手册是西格尼蒂克的工程师John G ‘Jack’ Curtis受到四十年代一些虚构幽默的真空管数据手册<ref>''Wemac 1Z2Z Slightly Tentative Data'', Eitel-McCullough, Inc. 1953, itself a successor to ''Umac 606 Infernal Anode Phantasatron Data Sheet'', Eitel-McCullough, Inc., 1950, both referenced on [http://www.sigwom.com/?p=186 "Wemac 1Z2Z Data Sheet", sigwom.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sigwom.com/?p=186 |date=20160223223041 }}. Note the reference to 'encabulitzation' in the 1Z2Z data sheet.</ref>笑话的启发，而开玩笑而创作的<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.sigwom.com/?page_id=17 | title = Sigwom | access-date = 2016-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160219044114/http://www.sigwom.com/?page_id=17 | archive-date = 2016-02-19 | dead-url = yes }}.</ref><ref name = Sigwom>{{Citation | url = http://www.sigwom.com/ | title = Sigwom | accessdate = 2016-02-19 | archive-date = 2019-01-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190123035308/http://www.sigwom.com/ | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。它的诞生被视为填补业界空白的“零的突破”，并且被故意收入在了西格尼蒂克的产品目录中<ref name = Sigwom />。随后，西格尼蒂克的公关人员Roy L Twitty在1973年4月1日发表了一篇大力兜售吹捧只写存储器的新闻稿。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.ariplex.com/tina/tsignet1.htm | editor = Tina | title = Funny pages | contribution = The original papers on the invention of the best electro… | accessdate = 2016-02-19 | archive-date = 2019-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190905130517/http://www.ariplex.com/tina/tsignet1.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

在25120型“全编码9046×N随机访问只写内存”的数据手册中，还包含了一些不同于常见特征曲线的夸张无意义曲线，例如“比特容量 vs. 温度”、“Iff vs. Vff”、“剩余的引脚数目 vs. 插入插槽的次数”，以及“可接受的质量标准 vs. 销售价格”。25120存储器需要6.3 VAC V<sub>ff</sub>（[[真空管|真空管]]灯丝）电压供应，+10 V<sub>cc</sub>（当时[[TTL|TTL]]的V<sub>cc</sub>的两倍），和一个零伏特的V<sub>dd</sub>（即接地），精度±2%。而指定的工作温度则是0到−70°C。<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Signetics | url = http://web.archive.org/web/20120316141638/http://www.national.com/rap/files/datasheet.pdf | title = Signetics 25120 Fully Encoded, 9046xN, Random Access Write-Only-Memory | first = John G ‘Jack’ | last = Curtis | year = 1972 | accessdate = 2012-03-16 | type = photocopy | format = PDF | archive-date = 2012-03-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120316141638/http://www.national.com/rap/files/datasheet.pdf }}.</ref>

== 苹果公司 ==
在1982年苹果官方出版的《Apple IIe 参考手册》（部件编号A2L2005）<ref>{{Citation | url = https://archive.org/details/a2_reference_manual | title = Apple IIe Reference Manual | publisher = Apple Computer | year = 1982 | id = part number A2L2005}}, 266 pp.</ref>中，对只写内存有两处提及。

第250页：
* ''只写内存：''一种可以存储信息，但永远不能从中检索信息的计算机内存。在1975年由教授Homberg T. Farnsfarfle与政府签订合同进行研发。Farnsfarfle的最初原型长宽约一英寸，至今已经被用于存储联邦政府超过100兆字的多余信息。批评者指责Farnsfarfle的项目毫无意义，浪费了超过600万美元。但他的支持者则指出，如果使用常规媒介来存储这些多余的信息则要花费多达2.5亿美元。

第233页：
* ''[[比特桶|比特桶]]：''所有信息最终安息的地方；参见''只写内存''。

== 书籍 ==
在1995年出版的书籍《计算机矛盾》中介绍了版权归爱尔兰商业机器公司（英语：Irish Business Machines，缩写：IBM）所有的可擦除式只写存储器（模仿[[可擦除可编程式只读存储器|可擦除可编程式只读存储器]]），写入这种存储器的数据随后可以擦除，以便重新利用存储空间。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=tZKCZje8178C&pg=PA69 | title = EWOM | format = Google books | page = 69}}.</ref>

随着在线浏览和个人观看的视频录像数据的爆炸性增长，但却缺少对视频数据档案进行搜索和检索的有效手段，则产生了另外一则流行的笑话，称录像带和其他视频媒介都属于只写内存，因为大多数视频因此在录制之后很少被再次观看。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=dRn5-nSYMwwC&pg=PA49 | title = Advances in Visual Information Systems: 4th International Conference, VISUAL... | format = Google books | page = 49}}.</ref><ref>{{Citation | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Fqk-eKrlFHkC&pg=PA61 | title =Forensic Digital Imaging and Photography | first1 = Herbert L | last1 = Blitzer | first2 = Jack | last2 = Jacobia | format = Google books | page = 61}}.</ref>

